         <div xml:lang="per" type="maintext" xml:id="orig_div2">
            <p>
               <lb/>غرض از این نوشته آنکه منکه
                  <persName ref="#anwarBeg">انور بیگ</persName>
                   ولد حیات بیگ و
               <persName ref="#sayyidAzam">سید اعظم</persName>
                ایم چنانچه
               <lb/>بموجب ورقه
               <gap/>
               خود دعوی درختان آنبه
               <lb/>در باغ
               <persName ref="#sahibRai">صاحب رای</persName>
               ولد دیانت رای
                نموده بودیم که پنج درختان
               <lb/>وغیره مایان در مذکور مومن الیه هستند موافق گفته اینجانب مشارالیه
               <lb/>سند درختان مزبور خواستند که سند آنبه ها از نزد خود
               <lb/>بر آورده بیارند تا اشجار آنبه بگیرند آنچه از نزد بنده
               <lb/>اسناد
               <gap/>
               <unclear>حاضر</unclear>
               نشده تا بنده باطل شد بنابرین
               <lb/>در محکمه پیش شریعت پناه فارخطی نوشته داده شد
               <lb/>که آینده دعوه اشجارها نمایم باطل است بنابران
               <lb/>قبل زمینداران و قانوگویان
               <persName ref="#pratapChand">پرتاب چند</persName>
               و
               <persName ref="#gulabRai">گلاب رای</persName> 
               و
               <lb/><unclear>پنجان</unclear>
               و
               <gap/>
               اقرار کرده می آید که آینده هیچ مناقشه
               <lb/>و خرخشه نیست و نمانده لهذا اینچند کلمه بموجب فارخطی
               <lb/>نوشته داده شد که ثانیاً حال سند باشد تحریر
               <lb/>فی تاریخ نوزدهم ماه رمضان المبارک سنه
               <date calendar="#fasli">۱۱۹۵</date><note>Unusually, the scribe has written the numbers from right to left, instead of the typical left to right order of numerals in Persian.</note>
               فصلی
               <lb/>یکهزار یکصد نود و پنج فصلی سمت
               یکهزار هشت صد
               <date calendar="#samvat-chaitradi">۱۸۴۵</date><note>As in the Fasli year above, here too, the scribe has written the numbers from right to left.</note>
               <lb/>چهل و پنج تحریر شد </p>
         </div>
            <div corresp="#orig_div2" xml:id="transdiv2">
               <p><lb/>The reason for writing this text is this, that we,
                  <persName ref="#anwarBeg">Anwar Beg</persName>,
                  son of Hayat Beg, and
                  <persName ref="#sayyidAzam">Sayyid Azam</persName>,
                  <lb/>had made a claim based on some documents to mango trees
                  <lb/>in the garden of
                  <persName ref="#sahibRai">Sahib Rai</persName>,
                  son of Dianat Rai, [specifically] that five trees, 
                  <lb/>etc., in the aforementioned place are ours. As said, the aforementioned person [<persName ref="#sahibRai">Sahib Rai</persName>]
                  <lb/>asked to see the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sanad">sanad</ref> of the aforesaid trees. [He said] that [if] we
                  <lb/>brought the documents, we could take the trees. Since
                  <lb/>the documents could not be presented, we were [our claim was] voided. On the
                  basis of this,
                  <lb/>in the court of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qazi">qazi</ref>, a <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_farighkhatti">farkhati</ref> was
                  written and given
                  <lb/>that if we make any claims to the trees in future, it will be void. On this
                  basis,
                  <lb/>in front of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_zamindar">zamindars</ref> and <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qanungo">qanungos</ref> <persName ref="#pratapChand">Pratap Chand</persName> and <persName ref="#gulabRai">Gulab Rai</persName> and
                  <lb/><unclear>the panchayat</unclear> and <gap/> an <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_iqrar">iqrar</ref> was made that henceforth there is no quarrel
                  <lb/>nor will it remain. Therefore, these few words were written as a <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_farighkhatti">farkhati</ref>
                  <lb/>[so] that it be a record for the future. 
                  <lb/>On the 19th of the month of Ramzan Mubarak in the year <date calendar="#fasli">1195</date> Fasli,
                  <lb/>[or] one thousand nine hundred and five <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_fasli">Fasli</ref>, [or] Samvat <date calendar="#samvat-chaitradi">1845</date> one thousand eight hundred
                  <lb/>forty-five,<note>Per ephemeris tables, the 19th of Ramzan during the Samvat-chaitradi year of 1845 fell on 23 June 1788.</note> it was written.
               </p>
            </div>

