            </div>
            <div corresp="#orig_div4" xml:id="transdiv4">
               <p>
                  <lb/>The slaves<note>The expression al-ʿabd literally means 'the slaves' but was used to indicate a countersignature or the signature of the parties making the declaration.</note>
                  <lb/><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_mirza">Mirza</ref> <persName ref="#anwarBeg">Anwar Beg</persName> son of Hayat Beg and <persName ref="#sayyidAzam">Sayyid Azam</persName>, 
                  <lb/>residents of <placeName ref="#dhar">Piran-i Dhar</placeName><note>Piran, literally 'holy men' is a short form of a common ephithet for the town of Dhar, meaning the abode of the light of the holy men.</note>
               </p>
